name: Interstellar (anaghkanungo7)
description:
Welcome to Interstellar - Sci-fi FPS Game

You wake up stranded on an alien moon base... the only way out is to find energy cells for your spaceship. However, there are intruders that you have to find and destroy on the way. The path is dangerous, will you survive or perish? 

Make your way through the rooms, collecting energy cells and defeating all enemies.
